  "body": "# Bug Report\r\nRemoval and adding to contacts of blocked user is synced only for the first removal/add to contact actions on paired devices. Following attempts of removal and adding to contacts of blocked user are not synced. \r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Create or restore an account on Device 1\r\n2) Restore the same account on Device 2 \r\n3) Pair Device 1 and Device 2 \r\n4) On Device 1 add any user to Blocked list (actual result: blocked user appears on Device 2)\r\n5) Open profile of Blocked user on both Devices\r\n6) Add blocked user to contacts on Device 1 (actual result: blocked user is added to contacts on Device 2)\r\n7) Remove blocked user from contacts on Device 1 (actual result: blocked user is added to contacts on Device 1)\r\n8) Once again add blocked user to contacts on Device 1\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior: \r\nBlocked user is NOT added to contacts on Device 2\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nBlocked user is added to contacts on Device 2\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/164024292-1675181b-9fc5-4fc6-8bd7-1c243d85dbf9.mp4\r\n\r\n[geth_device_1.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/8513756/geth_device_1.log)\r\n\r\n[geth_device_2.log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/8513782/geth_device_2.log)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
